%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Fgaming%2Fnews%2Fminecraft-studio-mojang-new-head-kayleen-walters-asa-bredin-1236304930%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20France%2C%20PM%20Visits%20Largest%20Scientific%20Project%20That%20Aims%20To%20Build%20Mini%20Sun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visited%20the%20ITER%20project%20or%20International%20Thermonuclear%20Experimental%20Reactor%20-%20which%20is%20described%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20and%20most%20expensive%20experiment%20on%20Earth%20-%20in%20Cadarache%20in%20southern%20France%20today.%20PM%20Modi%20was%20accompanied%20by%20his%20host%2C%20France%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron.%20A%20statement%20by%20India's%20foreign%20ministry%20termed%20it%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20ambitious%20fusion%20energy%20projects%20in%20the%20world%20today%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFusion%20Energy%20promises%20to%20offer%20an%20almost%20carbon-free%20and%20unlimited%20supply%20of%20clean%20energy%20and%20hence%20it%20is%20one%20futuristic%20solution%20to%20mitigate%20the%20threat%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20this%20visit%20to%20France%2C%20PM%20Modi%20inspected%20the%20most%20advanced%20fusion%20energy%20nuclear%20reactor%20where%20the%20world's%20seven%20most%20technologically%20advanced%20countries%20are%20collaboratively%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20miniature%20Sun%20on%20Earth%2C%20it%20has%20been%20named%20'The%20Way'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWent%20to%20the%20International%20Thermonuclear%20Experimental%20Reactor%20(ITER)%20in%20Cadarache%20with%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEmmanuelMacron%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40EmmanuelMacron%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Complimented%20the%20team%20working%20on%20this%20project%2C%20which%20represents%20a%20commendable%20step%20toward%20sustainable%20and%20limitless%20clean%20energy%20for%20the%20future.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLaBEpTIc3g%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLaBEpTIc3g%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1889662535051116994%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2012%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20it%20has%20'Made%20in%20India'%20written%20all%20over%20this%20project.%20India%20is%20contributing%20resources%20worth%20about%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crores%20or%20about%20%24%202.5%20billion%20to%20this%20effort%20and%20in%20return%20while%20contributing%20to%20less%20than%20ten%20percent%20of%20the%20cost%2C%20it%20will%20get%20access%20to%20one%20hundred%20percent%20of%20the%20intellectual%20property%20related%20to%20ITER.%20So%20that%20in%20future%2C%20a%20fusion%20energy%20reactor%20could%20actually%20be%20made%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20best%20nuclear%20scientists%20of%20the%20world%20are%20working%20in%20southern%20France%20to%20create%20'Aditya%20on%20Prithvi'.%20Efforts%20are%20on%20to%20simulate%20the%20nuclear%20reaction%20to%20power%20the%20Sun%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20visit%2C%20the%20leaders%20from%20India%20and%20France%20%26quot%3Bappreciated%20the%20progress%26quot%3B%20of%20ITER%2C%20including%20the%20assembly%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20Tokamak%2C%20where%20ultimately%20500%20MW%20of%20fusion%20power%20will%20be%20produced%20by%20creating%2C%20containing%20and%20controlling%20burning%20plasma.%20The%20leaders%20also%20appreciated%20the%20dedication%20of%20the%20ITER%20engineers%20and%20scientists%20working%20on%20the%20project.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20among%20the%20seven%20ITER%20members%20contributing%20to%20the%20project%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20Around%20200%20Indian%20scientists%20and%20associates%2C%20as%20well%20as%20notable%20industry%20players%20such%20as%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20Inox%20India%2C%20TCS%2C%20TCE%2C%20and%20HCL%20Technologies%2C%20among%20others%2C%20are%20engaged%20in%20the%20ITER%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%2C%20India's%20well-known%20heavy%20engineering%20company%2C%20is%20deeply%20involved%20with%20the%20ITER%20project%20and%20Anil%20Parab%2C%20a%20full-time%20Director%20at%20L%26amp%3BT%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBeing%20first%20of%20its%20kind%2C%20ITER%20fusion%20reactor%20brought%20out%20our%20best%20capabilities.%20The%20challenges%20involved%20led%20us%20to%20create%20new%20global%20benchmarks%20and%20develop%20advanced%20technologies%20as%20well%20as%20modular%20fabrication%20techniques%20to%20overcome%20logistic%20constraints.%20L%26amp%3BT%20showcased%20its%20state-of-the-art%20heavy%20engineering%20prowess%20at%20the%20global%20nuclear%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Parab%20added%20that%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20this%20biggest%20science%20project%20by%20delivering%20the%20world's%20largest%20and%20most%20complex%20stainless-steel%20high-vacuum%20pressure%20vessel%20called%20CRYOSTAT%2C%20nearly%20two%20years%20ahead%20of%20the%20project%20schedule.%20The%20Cryostat%20measures%20an%20impressive%2030%20meters%20in%20diameter%20and%20consists%20of%2054%20modules%20manufactured%20at%20L%26amp%3BT's%20AM%20Naik%20Heavy%20Engineering%20Complex%20at%20Hazira.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20life%20on%20Earth%20is%20sustained%20only%20because%20of%20a%20massive%20nuclear%20reactor%20-%20the%20Sun.%20It%20is%20a%20natural%20fusion%20energy%20cauldron%20and%20life%20on%20Earth%20would%20be%20impossible%20if%20solar%20energy%20came%20to%20a%20halt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reactor%20is%20likely%20to%20cost%20over%2022%20billion%20euros.%20The%20mega%20endeavour%20is%20to%20demonstrate%20first%20steps%20to%20harvest%20fusion%20energy%20which%20is%20to%20generate%20energy%20by%20fusing%20atoms.%20Traditional%20atomic%20energy%20works%20by%20splitting%20atoms%20and%20it%20generates%20long-lasting%20radioactive%20waste.%20But%20by%20fusing%20hydrogen%20and%20its%20sisters%20the%20waste%20product%20is%20a%20benign%20Helium%20gas.%20The%20Sun%20generates%20its%20energy%20by%20fusing%20atoms%20and%20today%20when%20climate%20change%20is%20bearing%20upon%20us%2C%20the%20search%20for%20clean%2C%20carbon%20free%20sources%20of%20energy%20is%20more%20important%20than%20ever.%20But%20making%20the%20Sun%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20partner%20nations%20are%20now%20co-operatively%20making%20the%20mini%20Sun.%20These%20countries%20are%20USA%2C%20Russia%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20China%2C%20India%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU).%20Since%20the%20massive%20reactor%20is%20being%20made%20at%20Cadarache%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20EU%20is%20taking%20care%20of%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20construction%2C%20rest%20of%20the%20member%20nations%20are%20sharing%209.1%20per%20cent%20cost%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20over%20a%20million%20different%20parts%20which%20will%20be%20sourced%20from%20over%2045%20countries%20and%20it%20is%20now%20estimated%20that%20by%202035%20the%20ITER%20machine%20will%20be%20ready%20for%20its%20first%20full%20experimental%20run.%20Currently%2C%20the%20ITER%20project%20is%20running%20way%20behind%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739366460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ft4b37jh_pm-modi-at-iter_625x300_12_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-france-prime-minister-narendra-modi-visits-largest-scientific-project-that-aims-to-build-mini-sun-7694951%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visited%20the%20ITER%20project%20or%20International%20Thermonuclear%20Experimental%20Reactor%20-%20which%20is%20described%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20and%20most%20expensive%20experiment%