%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f0314bf52b7bab8a6426%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222272%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20lots%20of%20things%20to%20avoid%20doing%20during%20work%20meetings.%3Cp%3EShakirov%20Albert%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-avoid-doing-at-company-holiday-party-etiquette-mistakes%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eetiquette%20expert%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20mistakes%20to%20avoid%20making%20during%20work%20meetings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20to%20avoid%20showing%20up%20late%2C%20multitasking%2C%20and%20dominating%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frules-for-holding-successful-virtual-meetings-with-employees%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evirtual%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20impolite%20to%20turn%20your%20camera%20off%20or%20send%20too%20many%20messages%20in%20the%20chat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20in-person%20or%20virtual%2C%20work%20meetings%20are%20almost%20always%20a%20guaranteed%20part%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-tips-for-changing-careers-finding-fulfilling-work-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprofessional%20life%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Unfortunately%2C%20employees%20can%20unintentionally%20undermine%20their%20professionalism%20during%20meetings%20in%20several%20ways.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20help%20you%20avoid%20these%20missteps%2C%20Business%20Insider%20asked%20etiquette%20expert%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcliseetiquette.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArden%20Clise%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20share%20some%20common%20mistakes%20people%20make%20during%20work%20meetings.%20Here's%20what%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aedeaff9-ea61-4950-b72d-76fa4db452f0%5C%22%3EShowing%20up%20late%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20meetings%2C%20a%20common%20faux%20pas%20is%20showing%20up%20late%20and%20disrespecting%20the%20time%20of%20others.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20everyone's%20arriving%20late%2C%20then%20you%20can't%20start%20a%20meeting%20on%20time%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20accomplish%20what%20you%20need%20to%20accomplish%2C%26quot%3B%20Clise%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClise%20told%20BI%20that%20she%20recommends%20facilitators%20always%20start%20the%20meetings%20on%20time%20to%20reward%20those%20who%20show%20up%20when%20they%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226945764f-cf13-489f-afde-61d4e704a115%5C%22%3ETurning%20the%20camera%20off%20in%20virtual%20meetings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227144%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20waving%20to%20her%20coworkers%20on%20a%20virtual%20meeting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761f1736c531c315b88d9ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225358%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDon't%20turn%20your%20camera%20off%20unless%20you%20have%20a%20specific%20reason%20for%20doing%20so.%3Cp%3EMorsa%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20virtual%20meeting%2C%20keeping%20your%20camera%20off%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20rude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20really%20disrespectful%20to%20just%20remain%20with%20your%20video%20off%20when%20you're%20addressed%20and%20when%20you%20are%20speaking%2C%26quot%3B%20Clise%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20there%20might%20be%20a%20few%20exceptions%2C%20like%20if%20your%20kid%20just%20came%20in%20the%20room%20or%20you%20have%20coworkers%20around%20you%2C%20but%20your%20camera%20should%20generally%20be%20on%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20you're%20talking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ba67d13-b43c-4305-92eb-2e6d35c759f9%5C%22%3ETrying%20to%20multitask%20during%20the%20meeting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Clise%2C%20it's%20not%20polite%20to%20juggle%20other%20tasks%20while%20in%20a%20meeting.%20This%20includes%20using%20your%20phone%2C%20jotting%20down%20notes%20unrelated%20to%20the%20meeting%2C%20or%20thinking%20about%20other%20to-do%20list%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20present%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20if%20you're%20doing%20other%20work%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20hear%20what's%20going%20on.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20participate%20because%20you're%20missing%20that%20opportunity%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Clise%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20she%20said%20to%20avoid%20anything%20that%20can%20pull%20your%20attention%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2fd339b-b5b8-4a36-bcb7-0326f3d269c2%5C%22%3EExcessively%20typing%20in%20the%20chat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-you-should-never-do-in-office-etiquette-coach-tips-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eetiquette%20mistake%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20avoid%20in%20virtual%20meetings%20is%20overusing%20the%20chat%20box.%20Clise%20said%20that%20continual%20messages%20can%20be%20distracting%20for%20others%2C%20so%20it's%20best%20to%20keep%20chat%20box%20usage%20to%20a%20minimum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20if%20you%20have%20a%20question%20for%20one%20person%2C%20sending%20them%20a%20direct%20message%20is%20much%20better%20than%20drawing%20everyone's%20attention%20to%20it%20in%20the%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChatting%20is%20like%20a%20side%20conversation%20in%20an%20in-person%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20Clise%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f96f575e-c74e-4285-9a33-35e63a582de4%5C%22%3EDominating%20the%20conversation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20board%20meeting%20with%20one%20person%20presenting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761f41f1d90e3bcf31d7566%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20important%20to%20give%20others%20the%20chance%20to%20talk.%3Cp%3EKlaus%20Vedfelt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20mistake%20to%20avoid%20is%20dominating%20the%20meeting%20and%20not%20allowing%20others%20to%20share%20their%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClise%20said%20it%20can%20be%20extremely%20frustrating%20if%20one%20person%20constantly%20shares%20ideas%20or%20asks%20questions%20without%20letting%20others%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-bllionaires-efficient-meetings-amazon-microsoft-apple-google-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20also%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20everyone%20is%20given%20a%20chance%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a13d10d-ad1f-4f9e-9c71-8b1f5ca39277%5C%22%3EInterrupting%20others%20while%20they're%20speaking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInterrupting%2C%20especially%20in%20virtual%20meetings%2C%20is%20a%20common%20misstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20sometimes%20in%20a%20meeting%2C%20particularly%20a%20virtual%20meeting%2C%20to%20know%20when%20someone%20is%20finished%20or%20going%20to%20be%20finished.%20But%20if%20you're%20someone%20who%20regularly%20interrupts%20people%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20can%20be%20really%20offensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Clise%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20it's%20accidental%2C%20it's%20essential%20to%20avoid%20talking%20over%20other%20people.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22904e2c40-b969-4cb2-965a-37b2ddf149b3%5C%22%3EPutting%20quiet%20team%20members%20on%20the%20spot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClise%20said%20it's%20never%20OK%20to%20point%20out%20that%20someone%20is%20quiet%20in%20a%20meeting.%20Doing%20so%20might%20make%20them%20feel%20uncomfortable%2C%20and%20it%20can