0Big%20Remark%20On%20Freebies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaking%20strong%20observations%20on%20the%20practice%20of%20political%20parties%20announcing%20freebies%20ahead%20of%20elections%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20people%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20willing%20to%20work%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20them%20and%20wondered%20whether%20a%20%26quot%3Bclass%20of%20parasites%26quot%3B%20was%20being%20created%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20matter%20on%20the%20right%20to%20shelter%20of%20homeless%20persons%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20AG%20Masih%20said%20people%20were%20getting%20ration%20and%20money%20without%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRather%20than%20promoting%20them%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20mainstream%20of%20the%20society%20by%20contributing%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20are%20we%20not%20creating%20a%20class%20of%20parasites%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulling%20no%20punches%2C%20Justice%20Gavai%20referred%20to%20the%20'Ladki%20Bahin'%20scheme%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20under%20which%20women%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2021-65%20with%20an%20annual%20family%20income%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20get%20Rs%201%2C500%20per%20month%20-%20and%20similar%20programmes%20run%20by%20ruling%20parties%20in%20other%20states%20and%20said%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20because%20of%20these%20freebies%2C%20which%20just%20on%20the%20anvil%20of%20elections%20are%20declared%2C%20like%20'Ladki%20Bahin'%20and%20other%20schemes%2C%20people%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20work...%20They%20are%20getting%20free%20ration%20and%20money%20without%20doing%20any%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20quite%20appreciate%20your%20concern%20for%20them%20but%20would%20it%20not%20be%20better%20to%20make%20them%20a%20part%20of%20the%20mainstream%20of%20society%20and%20permit%20them%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20nation%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%20there%20was%20hardly%20anybody%20in%20the%20country%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20work%20if%20they%20got%20work%2C%20he%20was%20interrupted%20by%20Justice%20Gavai%2C%20who%20went%20on%20to%20cite%20an%20example.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20be%20having%20only%20one-sided%20knowledge.%20I%20come%20from%20an%20agricultural%20family.%20Because%20of%20the%20freebies%20in%20Maharashtra%20which%20they%20announced%20just%20prior%20to%20elections%2C%20agriculturists%20are%20not%20getting%20labourers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Need%20For%20Balance'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20everybody%2C%20including%20Attorney%20General%20R%20Venkataramani%2C%20was%20on%20the%20same%20page%20that%20providing%20shelter%20to%20the%20homeless%20merited%20attention%20but%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20should%20it%20not%20be%20balanced%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Venkataramani%20said%20the%20Centre%20was%20finalising%20the%20urban%20poverty%20alleviation%20mission%2C%20which%20would%20tackle%20issues%20like%20providing%20shelter%20to%20the%20urban%20homeless.%20The%20bench%20asked%20the%20Attorney%20General%20for%20a%20timeline%20and%20also%20said%20the%20Centre%20should%20gather%20information%20from%20all%20states%20so%20that%20the%20issue%20could%20be%20considered%20on%20a%20pan-India%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20homeless%20was%20not%20being%20addressed%20as%20it%20was%20last%20on%20the%20priority%20and%20that%20the%20authorities%20showed%20compassion%20only%20for%20the%20rich%20and%20not%20the%20poor%2C%20his%20arguments%20were%20shot%20down%20by%20Justice%20Gavai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20make%20a%20political%20speech%20here.%20We%20won't%20permit%20our%20courtrooms%20to%20be%20converted%20into%20(an%20arena%20for)%20political%20battle...%20How%20do%20you%20say%20the%20compassion%20is%20shown%20only%20for%20the%20rich%3F%20Even%20for%20the%20government%2C%20how%20can%20you%20say%20this%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20now%20be%20heard%20after%20six%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20spoken%20out%20against%20freebies.%20In%20December%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20Justice%20Manmohan%20was%20surprised%20when%20it%20was%20informed%20by%20the%20Centre%20that%2081%20crore%20people%20are%20being%20given%20free%20or%20subsidised%20ration%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20of%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20migrant%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20receiving%20free%20ration%20since%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20how%20long%20can%20freebies%20be%20given%3F%20Why%20don't%20we%20work%20to%20create%20job%20opportunities%2C%20employment%20and%20capacity%20building%20for%20these%20migrant%20workers%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%20High%20Court's%20Refusal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20refused%20to%20hear%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20former%20judge%20against%20freebies%20promised%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%20on%20February%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20Justice%20SN%20Dhingra%20said%20such%20promises%20made%20by%20parties%20amounted%20to%20corrupt%20practices%20under%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act%20and%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20declare%20them%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B.%20The%20high%20court%20asked%20the%20former%20judge%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20it%20was%20told%20that%20a%20similar%20case%20was%20already%20pending%20before%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20distribution%20of%20freebies%20has%20also%20become%20a%20political%20issue%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20frequently%20attacked%20the%20AAP%2C%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20trying%20to%20buy%20people's%20votes%20by%20distributing%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Brevdis%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Hitting%20back%2C%20the%20parties%20have%20attacked%20the%20BJP-led%20government's%20track%20record%20on%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%20and%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20taxpayer%20money%20being%20used%20to%20make%20people's%20lives%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739363340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fgdemneb8_supreme-court_625x300_04_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-freebies-are-we-not-creating-class-of-parasites-top-courts-big-remark-on-freebies-7694511%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Making%20strong%20observations%20on%20the%20practice%20of%20political%20parties%20announcing%20freebies%20ahead%20of%20elections%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20people%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20willing%20to%20work%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20them%20and%20wondered%20whether%20a%20%26quot%3Bclass%20of%20parasites%26quot%3B%20was%20being%20created.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-freebies-are-we-not-creating-class-of-parasites-top-courts-big-remark-on-freebies-7694511%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Australian%20nurses%20'stood%20down'%20over%20video%20of%20anti-Semitic%20remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3