20times%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fliang-wenfeng-all-about-the-brain-behind-deepseek-7577547%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Liang%20Wenfeng%3A%20All%20About%20The%20Brain%20Behind%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20the%20Uyghurs%20facing%20a%20genocide%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20chatbot%20asserted%20the%20claim%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20slander%20of%20China's%20domestic%20affairs%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20unfounded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20firmly%20oppose%20any%20country%2C%20organisation%2C%20or%20individual%20using%20so-called%20human%20rights%20issues%20to%20interfere%20in%20China's%20internal%20affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ms%20Mahmut%2C%20%26quot%3Bso-called%20human%20rights%20issues%26quot%3B%20meant%20fleeing%20her%20hometown%20of%20Ghulia%20after%20seeing%20her%20neighbours%20and%20friends%20locked%20up%20en%20masse%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739362320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F462jmrq_uyghur-_625x300_12_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-deepseek-ai-covering-up-uyghur-genocide-report-7694325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rapid%20rise%20of%20China's%20DeepSeek%20AI%20chatbot%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20security%20concerns%20and%20allegations%20of%20censorship.%20Several%20countries%20have%20already%20banned%20its%20use%2C%20citing%20privacy%20and%20data%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-deepseek-ai-covering-up-uyghur-genocide-report-7694325%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Visits%20Cemetery%20In%20France's%20Marseille%2C%20Inaugurates%20Indian%20Consulate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20third%20and%20final%20day%20of%20his%20France%20visit%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20visited%20the%20historic%20Mazargues%20Cemetery%20in%20Marseille%20with%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Indian%20soldiers%20who%20fought%20in%20World%20War%20I%20and%20World%20War%20II%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20cremated%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20freedom%20fighter%20Veer%20Savarkar%20attempted%20a%20%26quot%3Bcourageous%20escape%26quot%3B%20in%20Marseille%2C%20PM%20Modi%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20India's%20quest%20for%20freedom%2C%20this%20city%20holds%20special%20significance.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20the%20great%20Veer%20Savarkar%20attempted%20a%20courageous%20escape.%20I%20also%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20people%20of%20Marseille%20and%20the%20French%20activists%20of%20that%20time%20who%20demanded%20that%20he%20not%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20British%20custody.%20The%20bravery%20of%20Veer%20Savarkar%20continues%20to%20inspire%20generations!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESavarkar%20had%20attempted%20his%20escape%20on%20July%208%2C%201910%2C%20from%20HMS%20Morea%2C%20by%20slipping%20through%20a%20porthole%20and%20swimming%20ashore.%20He%20was%20captured%20by%20French%20authorities%20and%20handed%20back%20to%20officials%20on%20the%20ship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20inaugurated%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20Marseille%20and%20said%20that%20it%20will%20deepen%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Macron%20and%20I%20reached%20Marseille%20a%20short%20while%20ago.%20This%20visit%20will%20witness%20important%20programmes%20aimed%20at%20further%20connecting%20India%20and%20France.%20The%20Indian%20consulate%20which%20is%20being%20inaugurated%20will%20deepen%20people-to-people%20linkages.%20I%20will%20also%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20Indian%20soldiers%20martyred%20in%20the%20First%20and%20Second%20World%20Wars%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20wrote%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20received%20a%20warm%20welcome%20from%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Marseille.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20staying%20here%20for%20the%20past%204%20years...%20I%20met%20PM%20Modi%20now...%20he%20was%20very%20happy%20to%20meet%20us%20and%20we%20also%20felt%20really%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20Priyanka%20Sharma%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20diaspora%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Macron%20also%20visited%20the%20International%20Thermonuclear%20Experimental%20Reactor%20(ITER)%20project%20in%20Cadarache%20in%20southern%20France.%20India%20has%20committed%20Rs%2017%2C500%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20project's%20cost.%20It%20has%20also%20contributed%20the%20biggest%20component%20in%20the%20project%20-%20the%20world's%20largest%20refrigerator%20that%20houses%20this%20unique%20reactor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Touched%20New%20Heights'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20said%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Macron%20travelled%20together%20to%20Marseille%20in%20the%20French%20presidential%20aircraft.%20Mr%20Misri%20termed%20this%20an%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20gesture%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bemblematic%20not%20only%20of%20the%20deep%20personal%20trust%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%20but%20the%20%26quot%3Bremarkable%20confidence%26quot%3B%20they%20have%20in%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20President%20held%20discussions%20on%20board%20the%20aircraft.%20You%20could%20say%20that%20India-France%20relations%20touched%20new%20heights%2C%20literally.%20And%20these%20discussions%20onboard%20the%20aircraft%20on%20a%20number%20of%20issues%20continued%20on%20landing%20in%20Marseille%2C%20where%20the%20two%20leaders%20were%20joined%20by%20their%20larger%20delegations...%20These%20discussions%20covered%20the%20entire%20gamut%20of%20our%20deep%20and%20diverse%20strategic%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Misri%20said%2C%20reviewed%20progress%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20defence%2C%20space%2C%20civil%20nuclear%20cooperation%2C%20health%20and%20people-to-people%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20secretary%20said%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20adopted%20a%20separate%20declaration%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20their%20key%20priorities%2C%20and%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Macron%20have%20also%20launched%20the%20logo%20of%20the%20India-France%20Year%20of%20Innovation%20in%202026.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnited%20States%20Next%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20left%20France%20for%20the%20United%20States%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%20(India%20time).%20He%20will%20be%20in%20the%20US%20for%20a%20two-day%20visit%2C%20during%20which%20he%20will%20meet%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20started%20his%20historic%20second%20term%20on%20January%2020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20will%20give%20further%20direction%20and%20momentum%20to%20this%20important%20partnership.%20We%20expect%20a%20joint%20statement%20to%20be%20adopted%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20visit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20said%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739362320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fvjsept9o_pm-modi-macron_625x300_12_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-france-visit-pm-france-visit-emmanuel-macron-pm-visits-cemetery-in-marseilles-france-inaugurates-indian-consulate-7693273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20third%20day%20of%20his%20France%20visit%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20visited%20the%20historic%20Mazargues%20Cemetery%20in%20Marseille%20with%20French%20