sofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcat-astrophe-at-30000-feet-stowaway-kitten-grounds-rome-to-germany-ryanair-flight-for-2-days%2Farticleshow%2F118177795.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118177795.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcat-astrophe-at-30000-feet-stowaway-kitten-grounds-rome-to-germany-ryanair-flight-for-2-days%2Farticleshow%2F118177795.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcat-astrophe-at-30000-feet-stowaway-kitten-grounds-rome-to-germany-ryanair-flight-for-2-days%2Famp_articleshow%2F118177795.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcat-astrophe-at-30000-feet-stowaway-kitten-grounds-rome-to-germany-ryanair-flight-for-2-days%2Famp_articleshow%2F118177795.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reader%20Friendly%2C%20Tables%20For%20Calculation%20Among%20Features%20Of%20New%20Income%20Tax%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20simplified%20Income%20Tax%20Bill%202025%2C%20which%20brings%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20'tax%20year'%20and%20abolishes%20the%20archaic%20and%20complicated%20terms%20'previous'%20and%20'assessment%20years'%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20comprises%20536%20sections%2C%2023%20chapters%20and%2016%20schedules%20in%20just%20622%20pages.%20It%20does%20not%20bring%20in%20any%20new%20taxes%2C%20but%20only%20simplifies%20the%20language%20of%20the%20existing%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%201961.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-decade%20old%20legislation%20has%20298%20sections%20and%2014%20schedules.%20It%20had%20880%20pages%20when%20the%20Act%20was%20introduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20replace%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%201961%20which%20has%20become%20too%20voluminous%20due%20to%20the%20amendments%20made%20over%20the%20last%2060%20years.%20The%20new%20law%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20April%201%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20bill%20has%20omitted%20redundant%20sections%2C%20like%20those%20relating%20to%20Fringe%20Benefit%20Tax.%20The%20Bill%20is%20free%20from%20'explanations%20or%20provisos'%2C%20thereby%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20read%20and%20comprehend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20word%20'notwithstanding'%2C%20which%20was%20used%20excessively%20in%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%201961%2C%20has%20been%20done%20away%20with%20in%20the%20new%20Bill%20and%20almost%20everywhere%20replaced%20with%20the%20term%20'irrespective'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20uses%20shorter%20sentences%20and%20has%20been%20made%20reader%20friendly%20with%20the%20use%20of%20tables%20and%20formulae.%20Tables%20have%20been%20provided%20for%20provisions%20relating%20to%20TDS%2C%20presumptive%20taxation%2C%20salaries%2C%20and%20deductions%20for%20bad%20debt%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Taxpayer's%20Charter'%20has%20been%20included%20in%20the%20Bill%20which%20outlines%20the%20rights%20and%20obligations%20of%20the%20taxpayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20replaces%20the%20term%20'previous%20year'%20as%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%201961%20with%20'tax%20year'.%20Also%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20assessment%20year%20has%20been%20done%20away%20with.%20Currently%2C%20for%20income%20earned%20in%20the%20previous%20year%20(say%202023-24)%2C%20tax%20is%20paid%20in%20assessment%20year%20(say%202024-25).%20This%20previous%20year%20and%20assessment%20year%20(AY)%20concept%20has%20been%20removed%20and%20only%20tax%20year%20under%20the%20simplified%20bill%20has%20been%20brought%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20likely%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Bill%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Finance%20for%20further%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Statement%20of%20Objects%20and%20Reasons%20of%20the%20new%20I-T%20Bill%20said%20that%20the%20Income-tax%20Act%20passed%20in%201961%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20numerous%20amendments%20since%20its%20passage%2060%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20these%20amendments%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Income-tax%20Act%20has%20been%20overburdened%20and%20language%20has%20become%20complex%2C%20increasing%20cost%20of%20compliance%20for%20taxpayers%20and%20hampering%20efficiency%20of%20direct-tax%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETax%20administrators%2C%20practitioners%20and%20taxpayers%20had%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20complicated%20provisions%20and%20structure%20of%20the%20Income-tax%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20government%20in%20the%20budget%20in%20July%202024%20announced%20that%20a%20time-bound%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20the%20Income-tax%20Act%2C%201961%20would%20be%20undertaken%20to%20make%20the%20Act%20concise%2C%20lucid%2C%20easy%20to%20read%20and%20understand.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20Income-tax%20Bill%2C%202025%20has%20been%20prepared%2C%20which%20proposes%20to%20repeal%20and%20replace%20the%20Income-tax%20Act%2C%201961.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Income%20Tax%20Bill%2C%202025%20comprises%20536%20sections%2C%20higher%20than%20298%20sections%20of%20the%20current%20Income-Tax%20Act%2C%201961.%20The%20existing%20law%20has%2014%20schedules%20which%20will%20increase%20to%2016%20in%20the%20new%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20number%20of%20chapters%20have%20been%20retained%20at%2023.%20The%20number%20of%20pages%20has%20been%20reduced%20substantially%20to%20622%2C%20almost%20half%20of%20the%20current%20voluminous%20Act%20which%20includes%20amendments%20made%20over%20the%20last%20six%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%201961%2C%20was%20brought%20in%2C%20it%20had%20880%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20clearer%20tax%20treatment%20on%20employees'%20stock%20options%20(ESOPs)%20have%20been%20included%20for%20reduced%20tax%20disputes%20and%20it%20includes%20judicial%20pronouncements%20of%20the%20last%2060%20years%20for%20more%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20income%20not%20forming%20part%20of%20total%20income%20have%20now%20been%20moved%20to%20schedules%20to%20simplify%20the%20statute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20Bill%2C%20Nangia%20Andersen%20LLP%20M%26amp%3BA%20Tax%20Partner%20Sandeep%20Jhunjhunwala%20said%20in%20the%20new%20bill%20all%20TDS%20related%20sections%20have%20been%20brought%20together%20under%20a%20single%20clause%20with%20simple%20tables%2C%20for%20ease%20of%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20mean%20post%20notification%20of%20this%20bill%20later%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20changes%20would%20be%20required%20in%20forms%20and%20utilities%2C%20for%20reporting%20purposes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20had%20announced%20in%20Budget%202025-26%20that%20the%20new%20tax%20bill%20will%20be%20introduced%20during%20the%20ongoing%20session%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20had%20first%20announced%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20the%20Income-tax%20Act%2C%201961%20in%20July%202024%20Budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBDT%20had%20set%20up%20an%20internal%20committee%20to%20oversee%20the%20review%20and%20make%20the%20Act%20concise%2C%20clear%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20understand%2C%20which%20will%20reduce%20disputes%2C%20litigations%2C%20and%20provide%20greater%20tax%20certainty%20to%20taxpayers.%20Also%2C%2022%20specialised%20sub-committees%20have%20been%20established%20to%20review%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20inputs%20and%20suggestions%20were%20invited%20in%20four%20categories%3A%20simplification%20of%20language%2C%20litigation%20reduction%2C%20compliance%20reduction%2C%20and%20redundant%2Fobsolete%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20income%20tax%20department%20has%20received%206%2C500%20suggestions%20from%20stakeholders%20on%20review%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739360820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fu7seq4t8_tds-vs-income-tax_625x300_09_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-income-tax-bill-brings-in-tax-year-concept-omits-assessment-year-7693788%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20simplified%20Income%20Tax%20Bill%202025%2C%20which%20brings%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20'tax%20year'%20and%20abolishes%20the%20archaic%20and%20complicated%20terms%20'previous'%20and%20'assessment%20years'%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-income-tax-bill-brings-in-tax-year-concept-omits-assessment-year-7693788%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJaiswal%20Plan%20Abandoned%26quot%3B%3A%20Gambhir%20Questioned%20Over%20Champions%20Trophy%20Squad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20final%20squad%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20beginning%20from%20February%2019%2C%20sprung%20a%20few%20surprises%20as%20marquee%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20snubbed%20for%20the%20tourn