reed%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20PTI%20during%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20at%20his%20ancestral%20home%20here%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Birbhum%20district%2C%20Sen%20also%20said%20that%20if%20secularism%20in%20India%20were%20to%20survive%2C%20there%20would%20not%20only%20have%20to%20be%20unity%20but%20also%20agreement%20on%20things%20that%20had%20made%20India%20an%20excellent%20example%20of%20pluralism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Delhi%20elections%20should%20be%20exaggerated%2C%20but%20it%20certainly%20has%20its%20significance.%20And%20if%20the%20AAP%20had%20won%20there%2C%20that%20victory%20would%20have%20carried%20its%20own%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Sen%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelving%20deeper%20into%20the%20reasons%20behind%20AAP's%20setback%2C%20the%20eminent%20economist%20said%20that%20one%20factor%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20unity%20among%20those%20who%20did%20not%20want%20a%20Hindutva-oriented%20government%20in%20Delhi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%20in%20many%20seats%2C%20the%20margin%20of%20BJP's%20advantage%20over%20the%20AAP%20was%20less%2C%20sometimes%20far%20less%2C%20than%20the%20votes%20that%20the%20Congress%20received%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20another%20important%20question%20is%20clarity%20with%20respect%20to%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20were%20the%20AAP's%20commitments%3F%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20AAP%20succeeded%20in%20making%20clear%20that%20it%20was%20firmly%20secular%20and%20for%20all%20Indians.%20There%20was%20too%20much%20catering%20to%20Hindutva.%20So%20it's%20not%20even%20clear%20how%20committed%20it%20was%20against%20religious%20communalism.%20The%20AAP%20didn't%20take%20clear%20sides%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Nobel%20laureate%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nonagenarian%2C%20however%2C%20praised%20the%20AAP%20for%20its%20efforts%20on%20school%20education%20and%20healthcare%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20Congress%20should%20have%20joined%20the%20party%20on%20those%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20daughter%20living%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20she%20and%20her%20family%20praise%20the%20AAP's%20efforts%20in%20the%20spheres%20of%20school%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20The%20Congress%20could%20have%20come%20together%20with%20the%20AAP%2C%20saying%2C%20'we%20like%20their%20schools%2C%20we%20like%20their%20hospitals%2C%20we%20want%20to%20extend%20them%2C%20and%20go%20beyond'.%20That%20would%20have%20been%20a%20better%20line%20than%20the%20one%20it%20took%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lack%20of%20focus%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20on%20public%20services%20in%20Delhi%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20the%20eventual%20electoral%20victors%20to%20focus%20instead%20on%20liquor%20licences%20and%20tax%20laws.%20AAP%20leaders%20were%20even%20held%20in%20custody%2C%20awaiting%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20said%20that%20the%20AAP%20could%20have%20focused%20more%20on%20issues%20of%20secularism%20as%20well%20as%20health%20care%20and%20education%20for%20all%20and%20could%20have%20done%20more%20to%20try%20and%20join%20hands%20with%20Congress%20on%20these.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20they%20were%20on%20different%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Sen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20is%20that%20this%20is%20a%20war%20that%20the%20AAP%20with%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20need%20not%20have%20lost.%20But%20they%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20there%20could%20be%20any%20impact%20of%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Delhi%20elections%20on%20Indian%20politics%2C%20the%20economist%20said%20that%20parties%20should%20be%20clear%20on%20where%20they%20stand%20and%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20indeed.%20I%20think%20the%20big%20impact%20may%20be%20on%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lesson%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20AAP's%20poll%20debacle%20is%20to%20reinforce%20to%20a%20great%20extent%20what%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20did%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20general%20election%2C%20namely%2C%20to%20take%20a%20clear%20stand%20against%20Hindutva%20politics.%20Most%20Indians%20don't%20want%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hoped%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Delhi%20election%20results%20would%20have%20the%20effect%20of%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20unity%20of%20vision.%26quot%3B%20Talking%20about%20whether%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Delhi%20polls%20could%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Bengal%20next%20year%2C%20Sen%20said%20every%20election%20in%20India%20has%20an%20impact%20on%20others%20and%20there%20could%20possibly%20be%20an%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Bengal%2C%20even%20though%20secular%20parties%20like%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20the%20CPI(M)%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20gone%20separate%20ways%2C%20there%20is%20still%20something%20of%20a%20social%20consensus%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20secularism%2C%20and%20also%20for%20education%20and%20health%20care%20for%20all%2C%20and%20even%20for%20social%20justice.%20I%20do%20not%20see%20a%20Delhi-type%20debacle%20happening%20in%20West%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSo%20yes%2C%20we%20have%20to%20watch%20out.%20But%20think%20dialectically.%20With%20greater%20focus%20on%20non-corrupt%2C%20honest%20governance%2C%20and%20a%20secular%2C%20justice-oriented%20and%20tolerant%20society%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20Bengal%20is%20in%20great%20danger%20of%20falling%20into%20a%20sectarian%20trap%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20economist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2091-year-old%20intellectual%20said%20that%20he%20dreamt%20of%20a%20united%20India%20moving%20faster%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20becoming%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wo