-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eour%20daughter%20was%20homeschooled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20bilingual%20(since%20there%20are%20no%20other%20American%20kids%20in%20her%20school%20and%20our%20daughter%20speaks%20Italian%20with%20an%20American%20accent)%2C%20she%20would%20have%20difficulty%20staying%20up%20to%20speed%20with%20the%20other%20kids.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20went%20to%20register%20her%20for%20school%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20bring%20our%20daughter%20in%20along%20with%20the%20work%20she%20had%20done%20at%20home%20for%20an%20evaluation.%20They%20needed%20to%20see%20if%20it%20would%20be%20possible%20to%20let%20her%20enter%20school%20mid-year%20since%20school%20had%20officially%20begun%20in%20September%2C%20and%20she%20would%20be%20starting%20in%20January.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20our%20daughter%20would%20be%20able%20to%20start%20school%20within%20a%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20daughter%20has%20been%20in%20school%20now%20for%20a%20little%20over%20three%20weeks%20and%20is%20doing%20amazing.%20Luckily%2C%20she%20entered%20a%20school%20where%20she%20already%20had%20so%20many%20friends%20in%20all%20different%20grades%2C%20so%20socializing%20was%20never%20a%20concern.%20She%20wakes%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20excited%20to%20go%20to%20school%2C%20gives%20me%20a%20kiss%2C%20and%20walks%20into%20the%20building%20proudly.%20She%20comes%20home%20happy%20from%20the%20long%20day%2C%20ready%20to%20do%20homework%2C%20and%20just%20as%20excited%20for%20the%20next%20day%20of%20school%20ahead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20often%20felt%20like%20people%20were%20questioning%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-decided-to-homeschool-my-children-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edecision%20to%20homeschool%20my%20chil