e%20culture%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECostco%20has%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20political%20crosshairs%20over%20DEI%2C%20and%20now%20some%20corporate%20leaders%20are%20left%20wondering%20who%20could%20be%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20some%20are%20choosing%20to%20make%20tweaks%20or%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Disney's%20HR%20chief%20told%20employees%20the%20company%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-is-latest-company-to-shake-up-dei-initiatives-memo-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erebranding%20its%20DEI%20metrics%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20programs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20changing%20the%20language%20of%20some%20content%20advisories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20last%20week%2C%20Google%20linked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ends-diversity-hiring-goals-reviews-dei-programs-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echanges%20to%20its%20DEI%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20concerns%20over%20compliance%20with%20executive%20orders%2C%20as%20the%20tech%20giant%20is%20a%20federal%20contractor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20many%20lawsuits%20and%20shareholder%20proposals%20against%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-shareholders-reject-anti-dei-proposal-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efailed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20highly%20publicized%20challenges%2C%20including%20executive%20orders%20from%20the%20White%20House%2C%20could%20still%20have%20a%20chilling%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20walking%20a%20line.%20They%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20into%20legal%20hot%20water%2C%20and%20yet%20they%20likely%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20retreating%20from%20the%20values%20they've%20espoused%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20experts%20%E2%80%94%20two%20lawyers%20and%20a%20business%20researcher%20%E2%80%94%20say%20the%20growing%20pressure%20on%20CEOs%20to%20eliminate%20their%20DEI%20practices%20might%20ultimately%20amount%20to%20little%20practical%20change%20in%20some%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20companies%2C%20most%20notably%20Costco%2C%20are%20digging%20in%20their%20heels%20in%20defense%20of%20DEI%2C%20others%2C%20like%20McDonald's%2C%20are%20taking%20a%20more%20conciliatory%20approach%20to%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252a97b7e-53f6-4039-9196-860a929353b3%5C%22%3EDEI%20policies%20get%20a%20facelift%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20changes%20companies%20make%20will%20likely%20boil%20down%20to%20how%20they%20communicate%20about%20their%20policies%2C%20both%20internally%20and%20externally%2C%20said%20Michael%20Thomas%2C%20a%20California%20attorney%20specializing%20in%20corporate%20diversity%20practices%20at%20the%20law%20firm%20Jackson%20Lewis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20said%20his%20firm%20has%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20requests%20from%20companies%20to%20review%20their%20DEI%20initiatives%20for%20legal%20risks%20from%20clients%20who%20are%20also%20concerned%20about%20how%20they%20are%20perceived%20by%20employees%20and%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20piece%20of%20the%20firm's%20legal%20review%20is%20examining%20how%20companies%20communicate%20about%20their%20policies%20and%20practices%20in%20websites%2C%20reports%2C%20and%20other%20filings%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20some%20of%20the%20changes%20at%20Disney%20appear%20to%20be%20more%20about%20how%20the%20company%20talks%20about%20DEI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20won't%20change%20is%20our%20commitment%20to%20fostering%20a%20company%20culture%20where%20everyone%20belongs%20and%20everyone%20can%20excel%2C%26quot%3B%20Disney's%20chief%20human%20resources%20officer%2C%20Sonia%20Coleman%2C%20said%20in%20a%20memo%20obtained%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmphasizing%20style%20more%20than%20substance%20could%20suggest%20a%20likely%20path%20forward%20for%20companies%20that%20see%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20as%20beneficial%20to%20their%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-latest-company-walk-back-dei-initiatives-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20McDonald's%20have%20conceded%20less%20than%20meets%20the%20eye%2C%26quot%3B%20Yale%20School%20of%20Management's%20Jeffrey%20Sonnenfeld%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20keeping%20the%20same%20principles%20and%20objectives.%20It's%20just%20a%20question%20of%20nomenclature%2C%20metrics%2C%20and%20bureaucracies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonalds%2C%20for%20example%2C%20said%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Four-stories%2Farticle%2Four-commitment-to-inclusion.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememo%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20franchisees%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20it%20was%20retiring%20%26quot%3Baspirational%20representation%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20swapping%20a%20broad%20vendor%20DEI%20pledge%20with%20direct%20discussions%20with%20suppliers%20about%20inclusion%2C%20and%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20its%20diversity%20team%20to%20be%20the%20Global%20Inclusion%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESonnenfeld%20pointed%20to%20the%20way%20terms%20like%20sustainability%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20and%20pollution%20abatement%20have%20cycled%20through%20the%20corporate%20lingo%20while%20generally%20sharing%20a%20common%20objective%20of%20protecting%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiversity%20and%20inclusion%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20have%20been%20around%20long%20enough%20at%20this%20point%20that%20they're%20often%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20corporate%20cultures%2C%20making%20it%20significantly%20harder%20to%20regulate%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20impossible%20to%20the%20point%20of%20insanity%20to%20try%20to%20ferret%20that%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20less%20modular%20it%20is%2C%20the%20less%20vulnerable%20they%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6f9a4f7-f50e-4afa-8074-448aefc003a6%5C%22%3ESome%20companies%20may%20pull%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20anti-DEI%20pressure%20could%20have%20other%20companies%20taking%20a%20more%20drastic%20shift%2C%20said%20Jon%20Solorzano%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20law%20firm%20Vinson%20%26amp%3B%20Elkins%20who%20advises%20public%20and%20private%20companies%20on%20areas%20related%20to%20ESG%20and%20risk%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20new%20administration%2C%20companies%20that%20may%20have%20been%20on%20the%20fence%20about%20DEI%20may%20decide%20to%20pull%20back%20some%20programs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferent%20companies%20view%20this%20differently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20that%20are%20probably%20in%20the%20more%20consumer-facing%20world%20are%20particularly%20sensitive%20to%20the%20reputational%20risks%20on%20both%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20major%20companies%20that%20BI%20has%20tracked%20as%20retreating%20on%20DEI%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20most%20follow%20a%20similar%20pattern%3A%20ending%20representation%20goals%20that%20could%20be%20construed%20as%20quotas%20for%20hiring%20or%20sourcing%2C%20halting%20participation%20in%20rankings%20and%20surveys%2C%20and%20reassigning%20DEI-focused%20staff%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20BI%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-vp-says-company-committed-to-dei-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20has%20changed%20the%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20website%20regarding%20DEI.%20A%20senior%20AWS%20executive%20told%20employees%20in%20her%20division%20that%20there%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bno%20changes%26quot%3B%20to%20key%20DEI-related%20benefits%2C%20including%20a%20transgender%20benefit%20offered%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20earlier%20in%20December%2C%20Amazon's%20VP%20of%20inclusive%20experiences%2C%20Candi%20Castleberry%2C%20said%20in%20a%20memo%20shared%20with%20BI%20that%20while%20the%20company%20was%20ending%20some%20%26quot%3Boutdated%26quot%3B%20programs%2C%20it%20was%20part%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bevolution%20to%20'built%20in'%20and%20'born%20inclusive%2C'%20instead%20of%20'bolted%20on.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20rebranding%20alone%20is%20not%20an%20option%20at%20federal%20agencies%20under%20Trump's%20rules%2C%20which%20require%20a%20deeper%20review%20of%20a%20program's%20history.%20Private%20companies%20aren't%20subject%20to%20that%20same%20level%20of%20government%20scrutiny%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now%2C%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Wednesday%2C%20newly%20sworn-in%20US%20Attorney%20General%20Pam%20Bondi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fag%2Fmedia%2F1388501%2Fdl%3Finline%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Justice%20Department%20intends%20to%20%26quot%3Binvestigate%2C%20eliminate%2C%20and%20penalize%20illegal%20DEI%20and%20DEIA%20preferences%2C%20mandates%2C%20policies%2C%20programs%2C%20and%20activities%20in%20the%20private%20sector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThey%20really%20need%20to%20balance%20those%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3ESolorzano%20said%20in%20reference%20to%20companies'%20decision-making.%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EWhat's%20more%20risky%2C%20the%20reputational%20harm%20of%20dealing%20with%20one%20of%20these%20investigations%20or%20having%20a%20mutiny%20of%20their%20employees%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f71c51a-7f79-4aea-9c1c-11bb21684904%5C%22%3EBusiness%20leaders%20make%20a%20case%20for%20diversity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%2C%20like%20Costco%2C%20has%20also%20taken%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-costco-keeping-dei-despite-trump-executive-orders-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20stand%20in%20defense%20of%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20is%20now%20the%20target%20of%20political%20and%20activist%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Jamie%20Dimon%20shrugged%20off%20an%20investor%20group's%20opposition%20to%20JPMorgan's%20DEI%20policies.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20bank%20started%20tracking%20executives'%20progress%20toward%20DEI%20goals%2C%20which%20affects%20their%20compensation%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20disclose%20publicly%20what%20proportion%20of%20executive%20pay%20is%20linked%20to%20DEI%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolorzano%20said%20he%20believes%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbifurcation%26quot%3B%20of%20companies%20over%20DEI.%20While%20many%20companies%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20adopted%20DEI%20programs%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20don't%20know%20that%20for%20every%20organization%20it%20was%20really%20core%20to%20their%20strategy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20places%20like%20Costco%2C%20it%20actually%20may%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Costco's%20December%20statement%20to%20shareholders%2C%20the%20board%20said%20diversity%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20bring%20originality%20and%20creativity%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20offerings%2C%20leading%20to%20greater%20satisfaction%20for%20its%20increasingly%20diverse%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%2019%20Republican%20state%20attorneys%20general%20last%20month%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-dei-letter-republican-attorneys-general-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20letter%20to%20Costco%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Ron%20Vachris%20expressing%20%26quot%3Bconcerns%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20company's%20compliance%20with%20changing%20state%20and%20federal%20laws.%20The%20AGs'%20letter%20doesn't%20identify%20any%20specific%20allegations%20of%20illegal%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolozano%20said%