I%20jumped%20into%20restaurants%2C%20where%20I%20spent%20almost%20eight%20years%20with%20Yum%20Brands.%20My%20last%20roles%20were%20Global%20Chief%20Marketing%20Officer%20and%20Chief%20Food%20Innovation%20Officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20moved%20to%20Wendy's%20to%20be%20CMO%20and%20spent%20my%20last%20four%20years%20of%20eight%20as%20the%20US%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20received%20some%20outreach%20from%20board%20members%20about%20the%20opportunity%20at%20TruGreen.%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20it%20would%20be%20the%20right%20match%20for%20me%2C%20but%20I%20talked%20with%20the%20board%20members%20about%20what%20TruGreen%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20many%20of%20the%20things%20I%20had%20done%20across%20all%20those%20other%20categories%20applied.%20It%20felt%20like%20an%20opportunity%20to%20lead%20a%20sleeping%20giant%20of%20a%20company%20that%20could%20explode%20in%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20a%20typical%20day%20has%20looked%20like%20since%20I%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7e362f0-99be-44b0-a67a-9a84dc927a0b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wake%20up%20at%205%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20business%2C%20customers%20are%20at%20our%20branches%20early%20to%20get%20out%20onto%20people's%20properties.%20I%20also%20try%20to%20model%20that%20by%20waking%20up%20at%205%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20wake%20up%2C%20I%20check%20our%20daily%20sales%20and%20performance%20reports%20before%20I%20go%20to%20the%20office%20to%20see%20what's%20happening%20with%20our%20business%20insights%20and%20analytics%20and%20how%20yesterday%20performed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicromanager-boss-this-is-what-i-learned-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicromanager%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it's%20helpful%20to%20see%20the%20trends%20and%20if%20the%20weeks%20are%20breaking%20the%20right%20way%20because%20we%20can%20influence%20outcomes%20on%20a%20week-to-we