essing%20environmental%20issue%20and%20find%20a%20sustainable%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaman%20was%20in%20his%20third%20year%20of%20BCom%20when%20he%20first%20noticed%20the%20ever-growing%20piles%20of%20discarded%20cigarette%20butts%20strewn%20across%20streets%2C%20parks%2C%20and%20public%20spaces%20around%20him.%20%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20went%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20cigarette%20butts%20was%20impossible%20to%20ignore.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20local%20problem%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20but%20one%20that%20spanned%20the%20entire%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20no%20adequate%20disposal%20systems%20in%20place%20and%20no%20regulations%20for%20recycling%20this%20waste.%20I%20realised%20this%20was%20a%20problem%20that%20needed%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Naman%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Vipul%2C%20co-founded%20Code%20Effort%20Private%20Limited.%20Together%2C%20they%20set%20out%20to%20create%20a%20new%20form%20of%20recycling%20technology%20that%20could%20transform%20cigarette%20stubs%20into%20reusable%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360462%2Feco-friendly-biodegradable-bags-plastic-bag-replacement-bioreform-startup-hyderabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally%20friendly%20materials%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCode%20Effort%20is%20the%20brainchild%20of%20my%20brother%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vipul%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20first%20shared%20his%20vision%20to%20combat%20the%20growing%20environmental%20crisis%20by%20recycling%20cigarette%20butts%2C%20I%20immediately%20believed%20in%20his%20mission.%20His