s-india-1738844473.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-1738844473-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-1738844473-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-1738844473-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fchangemakers-india-1738844473-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-404007%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Rare%20Diseases%20Care%20Coordination%20Centre%20(RDCCC)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20centres%20of%20excellence%20that%20has%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20government%20to%20help%20patients%20with%20rare%20disease%20treatment%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20initial%20resistance%20he%20was%20met%20with%20while%20appealing%20to%20different%20governments%20for%20medical%20funding%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThousands%20of%20children%20die%20of%20diarrhoea%20and%20malaria%20every%20year.%20Why%20should%20we%20give%20you%20money%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20he%20underlines%20the%20importance%20of%20not%20backing%20down.%20His%20tug-of-war%20with%20the%20bureaucracy%20lasted%20for%20six%20years%20from%202011%20to%202017%2C%20culminating%20in%20a%20sweet%20victory%20when%20Rs%20100%20crore%20was%20sanctioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%2C%20every%20patient%20with%20a%20rare%20disease%20(who%20qualifies%20based%20on%20the%20assessment%20criteria)%20would%20be%20entitled%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakh.%20The%20money%20would%20be%20directed%20to%20%E2