79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-404008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Rare%20Diseases%20Care%20Coordination%20Centre%20(RDCCC)%20has%20been%20designed%20by%20Prasanna%20Shirol%20to%20have%20a%20child-friendly%20environment%20that%20will%20make%20children%20comfortable%20during%20the%20treatment%20process%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMotivating%20a%20child%20for%20never-ending%2C%20long%2C%20and%20dreary%20hospital%20visits%20is%20a%20task%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prasanna%20points%20out.%20Having%20a%20new%20nurse%20perform%20the%20testing%20and%20therapy%20each%20time%20adds%20to%20the%20ordeal.%20At%20the%20RDCCC%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20that%20the%20staff%20is%20constant.%20Every%20time%20a%20child%20comes%20for%20treatment%2C%20they%20have%20a%20familiar%20face%20to%20look%20for.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20beautiful%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348647%2Fcancer-shelter-in-india-access-life-ankeet-dave-girish-nair-children-paediatric-care-in-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echild-friendly%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20comfortable%20waiting%20area%20makes%20it%20a%20pleasant%20experience%20for%20both%20the%20parent%20and%20child.%20The%20centre%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20patient%20turnout%20of%20275%2C%20has%20become%20a%20template%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Bengaluru%20centre%20is%20managed%20by%20them%2C%20there%20are%20ORDI%20coordinators%20stationed%20at%20the%20other%20centres%20of%20excellence%20too%2C%20to%20coordinate%20with%20hassled%20patients%20and%20parents%20and%20help%20them%20navigate%20the%20treatment%20process%20right%20from%20admission%20to%20fund%20access.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%2